<HL>
   Pier 1 Imports' Sales Increase
</HL>
<DATE>
08/16/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C8
</SO>
<CO>
   PIR
</CO>
<LP>
   FORT WORTH, Texas -- Pier 1 Imports Inc., a specialty
retailer, said its sales for the month ended Aug. 4 increased
16% to $45.9 million from $39.8 million a year earlier. Sales
at stores open at least one year rose 0.3%.
